      • style

        javafx.beans.property.Property<java.lang.String> style()

        Obtains the Property to the style sheet rules for the AdaptedChild.

        Note: this is NOT the style sheet URL. This is the style sheet rules (content of style sheet) and the AdaptedChild will handle making available to Parent as a URL.

        Returns:
